    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hero System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232480/extras/47232977c38d1f367fec947f09e46971.poster.avif?t=1772392106\" width=960 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232480/extras/47232977c38d1f367fec947f09e46971.webm?t=1772392106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232480/extras/47232977c38d1f367fec947f09e46971.mp4?t=1772392106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assign <strong>Heroes</strong> to your turrets to completely overhaul their performance. This adds a critical layer of tactical depth. Each hero features unique specializations: from buffing adjacent towers and boosting resource extraction to wielding devastating fire elements. Your choice of hero dictates your entire strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Modules</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232480/extras/7b51b12394884b9f9510a68a013f417d.poster.avif?t=1772392106\" width=960 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232480/extras/7b51b12394884b9f9510a68a013f417d.webm?t=1772392106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232480/extras/7b51b12394884b9f9510a68a013f417d.mp4?t=1772392106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s not just about building and upgrading turrets. Combine them with <strong>Modules</strong> — a deep upgrade system that fundamentally alters turret functionality, offering infinite build variety and massive replayability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Abilities</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232480/extras/15919f8e312cccc44f5c028440e9592c.poster.avif?t=1772392106\" width=960 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232480/extras/15919f8e312cccc44f5c028440e9592c.webm?t=1772392106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232480/extras/15919f8e312cccc44f5c028440e9592c.mp4?t=1772392106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash powerful <strong>Ability Cards</strong> to turn the tide of battle. Incinerate waves with a wall of fire, weaken enemies for the upcoming round, or supercharge a turret at the cost of sacrificing its neighbors. Experiment with synergies to find the ultimate winning combo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
